snippet.title: SRB2 Top Down - Frozen Factory
snippet.description:
We play a preview of Frozen Factory Zone, a map by Chromatian that'll also be available in the demo. This time we make mistakes for once in a video. Also ugh video quality.

Read the fucking description.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

https://mb.srb2.org/showthread.php?t=38088

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Iceman404 - Sonic

Sryder13 - Tails

Chromatian - Knuckles

---------------------------------------------------------------------------

Level theme - Sonic Lost Worlds, Frozen Factory Zone

Spring Yard Zone Elevator theme by - Karl Brueggemann

Team Death jingle - Kirby 64, Crystal Shards 

Final Fantasy 7 Game Over (demo only) theme by - Smooth McGroove + OneyG




THAT THEME IS NOT VIDEO EDITED IT WILL ACTUALLY PLAY
